                        </figure>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-6">
                        <div class="tm-description-box">
                            <h4 class="tm-gallery-title">Why Hook On Books? </h4>
                            <p class="tm-mb-45">
                                Think about the last good book you read. Did it make you feel more connected to others?
                                Maybe it served as a welcome escape. Maybe it helped you rediscover the beauty in life. Did it surprise you?
                                <br />
                                As an online bookstore, we strive to offer the same variety and richness of experience as the books on our shelves to your doorstep.
                We've been in the online shopping business for many years so we know what we are doing,
                                and we guarantee that you can trust us, our products and our service.
                            </p>
                            <a href="about.html" class="tm-btn tm-btn-default tm-right">Read More</a>
